            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8357174/">鹅？西游记是一个黑暗文本？？</a></h2>

                <div id="review_8357174_short" class="review-short" data-rid="8357174">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        这篇文章意图反驳两种西游解读：  ——《西游记》是一个“黑暗的恐怖故事”，反映了人性最黑暗的部分；周星驰拍的暗黑西游才是“真正的西游记”。  ——孙悟空是一个反抗失败的悲剧英雄；唐僧是“封建大家长”；《西游记》是在反叛的外衣下宣扬“封建伦理纲常”；周星驰的颠覆...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8357174-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_8357174_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_8357174_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="8357174" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-8357174">
                                1652
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="8357174" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-8357174">
                                87
